{"tid":1598592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[929行動post] 929 全球自由鳥大集會","createTime":"2019-09-27T14:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:14:13.000Z","uid":51338,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac9d81fe61d75ac694c01e6c180f571ac9eabd0","tid":1598592,"uid":51338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"929當日, Freenix Team會於14:00舉辦&quot;自由鳥快閃銅鑼灣&quot;, 當日請帶上你的自由鳥, 詳情請留意Freenix公海於929 12:00宣布。<br />\n<br />\n面對强權, 面對黑暗, 縱使未方便出席遊行, 也能以自由鳥作多元化抗爭, 請把你的自由鳥放到地區的連儂牆, 讓香港18區百鳥齊放, 讓世界看見香港人強大的信念。 <br />\n<br />\n這幾天對於香港人來說, 是一個又一個的表達機會, 同時也是一個又一個的難關。 希望香港人能勇敢站出來的同時, 保持警覺, 一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n香港人, 萬事小心。 保重。<br />\n<br />\n請支持<br />\n#freenix<br />\n#birdfoldingchallenge<br />\n#929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Freenix TG 公海</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/FreenixthefreebirdHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFreenixthefreebirdHK&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHe6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=da332793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/FreenixthefreebirdHK</a><br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Freenix the Freebird Production Crew Presents:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8g3mc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8g3mc3.jpg&h=edf52562&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8H6Sex5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8H6Sex5.jpg&h=816f77bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8uR63rq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8uR63rq.jpg&h=471e2767&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rw7h96r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRw7h96r.jpg&h=f942ef85&s={SIZE}\" /><img s